PortSystem          1.0
PortGroup           golang 1.0

go.setup            github.com/anchore/grype 0.38.0 v
github.tarball_from archive
revision            0

description         \
    A vulnerability scanner for container images and filesystems

long_description    \
    A vulnerability scanner for container images and filesystems. Works with \
    Syft, the powerful SBOM (software bill of materials) tool for container \
    images and filesystems.

categories          security
installs_libs       no
license             Apache-2
maintainers         {gmail.com:herby.gillot @herbygillot} \
                    openmaintainer

checksums           rmd160  12f5f9bee78746d72dc8403bfe1f0519f0969d4b \
